HEADWORD: Stunner
<hw>Stun"ner</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, stuns.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Something striking or amazing in quality; something
of extraordinary excellence.</def> <mark>[Slang]</mark>
<rj><au>Thackeray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stunning</ent>⟦br⟧
